'''天主教伊瓦格總教區'''（{{lang-la|Arcidioecesis Ibaguensis}}；{{lang-es|Arquidiócesis de Ibagué}}）是[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[總教區|總教區]]，下轄五個教區。

教區於1900年5月20日成立，1974年12月14日升為總教區<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |volume=LXVII |year=1975 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=167-168 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-67-1975-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-05-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529181815/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-67-1975-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-05-29 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

總教區管轄[[托利馬省|托利馬省]]北部，2006年時有504,310名教友（佔轄區總人口90.0%）。教區下轄55個[[堂區|堂區]]和101名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任總主教為{{link-de|賀朗·羅阿-巴爾沃薩|Orlando Roa Barbosa}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 29.05.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/29/200529b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-05-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529120142/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/29/200529b.html |archivedate=2020-05-29 |language=en |date=2020-05-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|彌額爾·威田南·貢薩萊斯-馬里尼奧|Miguel Fernando González Mariño}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 11.02.2016 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2016/02/11/0104/00261.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-05-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529173117/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2016/02/11/0104/00261.html |archivedate=2020-05-29 |language=it |date=2016-02-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-es|弗拉維奧·卡列·薩帕塔|Flavio Calle Zapata}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 20.03.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/03/20/190320e.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-04-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430060931/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/03/20/190320e.html |archivedate=2019-04-30 |language=en |date=2019-03-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

